        </item>
        <item>
            <title>醫管局科技全面升級，地理圍欄防病患走失、智能氧氣樽提示醫護換樽</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/01/ha-geo-fence/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ha-geo-fence</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/01/ha-geo-fence/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 05:20:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1300593</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>醫院管理局（醫管局）推出多項科技措施，提升醫療服務質素。其中急症室陸續安裝地理圍欄定位系統，預計 2025 年底前全面啟用，防止病人走失。此外瑪麗醫院重建項目首階段將於今年內投用，引入智能藥櫃提升藥物管理效率。智能氧氣樽則計劃擴展至所有醫管局服務，確保氣體及電池狀態受監控。電子化共通平台已於去年底推行至全線醫院，取代紙本記錄紗布使用情況，並將進一步開發傷口評估功能。新一代早期事故通報系統亦即將推出，結合人工智能分析，促進員工反饋。</p><h2>地理圍欄定位系統：守護病人安全</h2><p>醫管局為應對病人走失問題，在急症室引入地理圍欄定位系統。系統透過藍牙手帶監測病人位置，特別針對精神或認知障礙者。若病人接近出口，系統會發出警報，協助醫護人員及時介入。據醫管局資料，18 間公立醫院急症室將於 2025 年底前完成安裝。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300594" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123037-694x437.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="437" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123037-694x437.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123037.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲地理圍欄定位系統藍牙手帶，圖片來源：RTHK</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300595" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123041-694x447.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="447" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123041-694x447.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123041.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲地理圍欄定位系統藍牙手帶，圖片來源：RTHK</p><h2>智能裝置提升效率</h2><p>瑪麗醫院重建項目第一期病房將於 2025 年內啟用，新增智能藥櫃，讓非辦公時間的藥物存取更安全及快捷。智能氧氣樽同時現已應用於非緊急救護車服務，未來將推廣至所有醫管局服務範圍。智能氧氣樽能在氧氣或電池不足時發出警報，確保病人安全。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300596" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123124-694x458.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123124-694x458.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123124.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲智能氧氣樽（右），圖片來源：RTHK</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300598" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123108-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123108-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123108.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲智能氧氣樽，圖片來源：RTHK</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300599" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123510-694x454.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="454" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123510-694x454.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123510.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲智能氧氣樽，圖片來源：RTHK</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
