            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>廣汽集團旗下全新 SUV 型號 AION V 今日正式登陸香港市場，搭配 400V 快充及第二代彈匣電池技術，續航力最高可達 602 公里，突破平價家庭電動車的續航距離。AION V 將推出 Premium 與 Luxury 兩個版本，售價分別為 HK$218,000 及 HK$238,000 起。</p><figure id="attachment_1300435" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1300435" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300435" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144529-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144529-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144529-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1300435" class="wp-caption-text"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300434" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_150131-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_150131-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_150131-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></figcaption></figure><p>第二代 AION V 採用 FWD 前輪驅動，最大功率為 100kW，扭力可達 240Nm，新車提供兩種規格選擇，Premium 和 Luxury 版本的電池容量為 64.5kWh 及 75.26kWh 續航力分別為 505 公里及 602 公里，滿足不同用戶的出行需求。全系 AION V 採用磷酸鐵鋰（LFP）電池，支持 3C 快充技術，最快可於 16 分鐘把電池由 30% 充至 80%，充電時間得以縮短。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300429 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144824-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144824-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144824-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><figure id="attachment_1300440" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1300440" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300440" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144801-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144801-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144801-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1300440" class="wp-caption-text"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300430 aligncenter" style="font-size: 16px;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144836-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144836-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144836-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></figcaption></figure><p>AION V 另一個賣點是提供多項針對家庭用戶需要的設計，隨車設有可電暖、通風與按摩的前座，後排椅背可向後調整至 20 度，更設有一鍵躺平功能，結合三層式特大車尾儲物箱與車載冰箱，讓駕乘體驗更貼近家庭出行需要。AION V 車身尺寸為: 4605mm x 1876mm x 1686mm，長達 2775mm 的軸距為同級車中最長，後排腿部空間達 1040mm，設計寬敞，新車同時加入智能四音區語音識別系統，能根據乘客座位辨識指令，提供個人化娛樂控制。此外，AION V 配備雙前氣袋及雙前側氣袋、前座中央氣袋及兩側 2.3 米超長車側氣袋，加上標準配置的 ACC 定速巡航、AEB 主動式緊急剎車、BSD 盲點提示、ELKA 越線提示及輔助等，安全功能相當豐富。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300431 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144906-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144906-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144906-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300432 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144936-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144936-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144936-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1300433 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144948_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144948_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144948_-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>內飾設計簡約，配備 8.88 吋全液晶儀表和 14.6 吋中控屏幕，車門把手、空調出風口等細節採用金屬裝飾，提升質感。Luxury 版本配備皮質座椅，主駕座椅支持電動調節，後排座椅靠背角度可調至 137 度，並可實現 4/6 比例折疊及齊平放倒，增加實用性。​在配置上，Luxury 版較 Premium 版提供更多高級功能。​例如，Luxury 版提供冷暖冰箱、配備比利時 Premium 頂級音響系統，包括三分頻設計和 8 吋重低音揚聲器，提供更佳的音質和空間感。​此外，Luxury 版還可能配備感應式電動尾門、前排座椅記憶、通風加熱功能，以及前排座椅按摩等高級配置，進一步提升舒適性和便利性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300436" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144653-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144653-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144653-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300437" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144659-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144659-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144659-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300441" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144924-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144924-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250331_144924-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">AION V Premium 及 Luxury 版的零售價分別為 218,000 港元及 238,000 港元，於早鳥期內訂購更可享高達 10,000 港元折扣</p><p>​來源: 新聞稿</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
